    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/75c73f24dd99289c91b005f859e4f587.poster.avif?t=1754448351\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/75c73f24dd99289c91b005f859e4f587.webm?t=1754448351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Castillo: The Nine Circles</strong> 是一款复古 FPS 收集马拉松，融合了 90 年代平台游戏的探索与 90 年代最佳射击游戏中您喜爱的所有屠杀。收集隐藏在每个地狱圈中的能量碎片，以解锁中心的新区域并打开 9 个不同的世界。<br><br>你的凶手已经回到过去来折磨你过去的自己，即使他必须撕裂时间才能把你留在那里。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/9432f48a873857a31d97b3bf39c31478.poster.avif?t=1754448351\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/9432f48a873857a31d97b3bf39c31478.webm?t=1754448351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>解锁独特的能力，让穿越每个世界变得更加容易。<br></li><li>使用致命武器消灭大量怪物。<br></li><li>建立大型连击以提高速度。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/1e9e5f8756e33c68bd58312b8be0a76b.poster.avif?t=1754448351\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293880/extras/1e9e5f8756e33c68bd58312b8be0a76b.webm?t=1754448351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>让自己沉浸在地狱的 9 个圆圈中，每个圆圈的灵感都来自但丁的《地狱篇》，并且充满了秘密。<br></li><li>遇见令人难忘的角色以及一大群闪亮的收藏品。</li></ul>",
